I set this view of AI, espoused by Google and Facebook, in contrast to the =
vision of computing espoused by Microsoft and Apple; here my anchor was Mic=
rosoft=E2=80=99s 2018 Build keynote:

Earlier this week, while delivering Microsoft=E2=80=99s Build conference ke=
ynote, CEO Satya Nadella struck a very different tone; after describing how=
