ions. And so we need to develop a set of principles that guide the choices =
we make because the choices we make is what=E2=80=99s going to define the f=
uture=E2=80=A6

This opportunity and responsibility is what grounds us in our mission to em=
power every person and every organization on the planet to achieve more. We=
=E2=80=99re focused on building technology so that we can empower others to=
