has become so second nature in our digital lives that we often don=E2=80=99=
t even realize or recognize it.

You could say we=E2=80=99ve been using AI on autopilot, and now this next g=
eneration of AI, we=E2=80=99re moving from autopilot to copilot. We=E2=80=
