=E2=80=99s implementation ( https://www.theverge.com/2023/3/14/23639273/goo=
gle-ai-features-docs-gmail-slides-sheets-workspace ) will be at least compa=
rable. The problem with the Workspace + vertical SaaS app stack, though, is=
